Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:22.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清风　云彩　仰望群星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:30.98,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中的悸动　如波涛汹涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:38.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无穷　无尽　战火连绵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:46.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等扬帆　即日踏上征途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:53.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有暗阎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:01:01.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻塞前行之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:13.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥想　祈福　唯愿君平安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:28.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0}向无尽宇宙{\fsp-9}、{\fsp1.5}出征
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.72,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:10.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:28.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:50.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:24:01.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之剑{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斩断这一昏暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:08.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩这点了吗 罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着急也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定几时就冒出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必他还在为莉拉的事耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算智商过人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情商却和普通人没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是仿照卡萨比安卡旅馆建的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口看到的景象也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和艾里亚完全不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}カレン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 它都这么旧了 你还很珍惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.31,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是心上人送的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我困了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1320,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}如沧海一粟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么新情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被假情报骗了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还要灰溜溜地无功而返
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 再拖延下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此前 维尔达纳的叛乱份子已经被渚士朗除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你躲到哪里 我都要把你揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚正在为成为维尔达纳宫廷贵族谋反牺牲品的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯特拉德侯爵举行肃穆的葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在葬礼上 亚术曼藩王殿下亲致悼词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝都人人悼念艾斯特拉德卿 为其服丧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜好像认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 看起来不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 接下来要靠走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也没有目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先住在我家好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔 不会打扰到你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知该说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾宾格王国就像我的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于身为人质的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在梦中重回故土了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也少了一份迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父王说过 只要没有迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野就会豁然开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是好事 法尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事啊 贝鲁提耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 下官被夹伤了脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所幸乘救生艇漂流时被护卫舰所救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,923)\fad(500,500)}贝鲁提耶大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(734,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ベルティエ大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利已经不在正直老人号上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官正动用一切手段全力搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能赶在哲力胥阁下之前找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为成事可以不择手段 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有下一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体追击应该交给失去弟弟的哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是人情之常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们近卫军只是在搜索方修利的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就应该将此事通知哲力胥卿 共同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以哲力胥卿的性格 不可能接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可能使事态复杂化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿居然平添一个同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴吗 未必
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如藩王殿下所说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就静观其变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 您一扫维尔达纳宫廷贵族的手段真是高明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是您放风诱敌的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果比想象中更加严重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 泰坦尼亚都是借此延续权力与繁荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能您最为适任…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔大婶都是我的远亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就在他们家叨扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我家在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我自己建的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己动手 丰衣足食嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己建的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托马斯大叔也帮过忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在之前艾里亚内乱时死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是艾里亚时的老朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}卡特丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}カトリーヌ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你也从艾里亚来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜受关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我才没麻烦过他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}托马斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}トーマス
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和卡特丽奴正是在卡萨比安卡归入泰坦尼亚时认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我慌不择路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就逃进了卡特丽奴家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不要多嘴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人陪托马斯大叔说话 他高兴着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 原料都是早晨刚到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧 可怜特制蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:09:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢蛋包饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你要带我去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的 散步罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在高处很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服是舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要多久才到？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个男人没错？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在山里见过 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现疑似方修利的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人在卡萨比安卡E地区
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时 提到方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此等风景还真难得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我寂寞悲伤的时候都会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现方修利了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报属实？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在卡萨比安卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官马上联系哲力胥阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他追捕方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿曾被虚假情报蒙骗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子全失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若再重蹈覆辙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不容有失…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到方修利之后再禀报他即可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄 这个真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要连我的份一起吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你不要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派最接近卡萨比安卡的友军前往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 就到山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经派兵前去抓捕方修利了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 照您的指示办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 方修利那家伙也完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 很壮观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 来对了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 我眼睁睁地看着她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想害你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 我只是回忆起过去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 忆起了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过生日时妈妈给的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装在里面的麦粒是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论身在何处 只要种下它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会萌发出生命之芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若不播种 就只是单纯的麦粒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若遇到困难 灰心丧气的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看它 从中汲取勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是小小的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它们肯定会让可怜心生幸福之芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论何时 都要向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯愿可怜永远开朗 永远健康
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有个好妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望所在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能把你交给泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然妈妈死后我也曾消沉过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到这个 我涌起了活下去的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想办法来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以分给我一粒小麦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 一粒就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样嚼麦粒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被施了魔法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气马上涌上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在播耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来的曲子是不见不散的这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空为粉色所染
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳在云端露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的发色相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么歌词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日之事过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用泪水拭去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是新一页
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空白等你来书写
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该用什么蜡笔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:19:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要消沉到什么时候啊 方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是暖色比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够绘出什么画
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要留待梦中见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄也来吧 很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄跳得真烂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是第一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦粒的回礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 就用这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的我也只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好久没这样笑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要怎么办 垂头丧气的英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有它在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后有机会 我还帮你擦鞋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 做你的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正找的方修利在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢包庇他有你好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在附近见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会因为戴着帽子所以被误认了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我和英雄一起散过步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手续都办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是好人呢 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你也是个好人 我们放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督在千钧一发之际逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝鲁提耶大佐的一再失败触怒了伊德里斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 请您安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请随我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我求生不得 求死不能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此后 贝鲁提耶大佐的名字再也没有出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到了同伴身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去筹集军费了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很有行骗的才能？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(650,345)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}反击的烽火


